Meet Doll and baby Dot! I am blessed to get to foster them for @deityanimalrescue. Baby dot somehow got severely burned on her feet and tail before they were saved and were pretty sure there were other puppy’s that didn’t make it. So far a part of baby dots tail fell off due to the trauma from the injury and we’re keeping close watch making sure she’s thriving! Mama doll is an amazing beautiful mama💕 They will both be avail for adoption when they are healed and the baby Dot is 8 weeks . Follow @deityanimalrescue for details or applications to adopt xxeg 💕❤️ #Tommypickles also a baby :) #fostersaveslives
